---
import SectionTitle from '../common/SectionTitle.astro';
---

<section id="target" class="section-padding bg-bg-secondary">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <SectionTitle class="fade-in-up">
        こんな方にぴったりです
      </SectionTitle>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-10 shadow-md fade-in-up">
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 stagger-item">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-pink/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-gray-800 text-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">マッチングアプリに少し疲れてきた</span>
            </span>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 stagger-item">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-pink/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-gray-800 text-lg">
              プロフィールやメッセージだけでは<span class="font-bold">相性が分からない</span>と感じている
            </span>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 stagger-item">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-pink/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-gray-800 text-lg">
              まずは<span class="font-bold">"一度会って話してみたい"</span>という感覚を大事にしたい
            </span>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 stagger-item">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-pink/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-gray-800 text-lg">
              真剣だけど、<span class="font-bold">ガチガチの婚活パーティーは少し抵抗がある</span>
            </span>
          </li>

          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 stagger-item">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-pink/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-pink" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-gray-800 text-lg">
              <span class="font-bold">30〜40代の同年代</span>と、落ち着いた雰囲気で話したい
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .shadow-md {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
</style>
